Here's what Phoenix V4 does:\
\
Phoenix V4 is a deterministic content assembly engine for producing therapeutic self-help books at scale \'97 without AI ever writing the prose. Its core philosophy: humans create meaning, machines enforce structure, runtime only assembles.\
\
How it works in a nutshell: Human authors write all the actual content (stories, exercises, reflections). That content gets decomposed into small, role-tagged "atoms" (60\'96150 words each), linted against strict quality rules, and approved into a pool. At runtime, V4's compiler selects and orders those pre-approved atoms into full books \'97 it never generates, rewrites, or paraphrases anything.\
\
The 5-stage pipeline:\
\
Catalog Planner \'97 takes inputs like topic (anxiety, burnout, etc.), persona (gen-z professional, new mom, etc.), and brand, then produces a BookSpec.\
Format Selector \'97 maps that spec to a structural format (one of 15 beat-map families across 3 tiers: full books, micro-books, rescue kits) with exact slot definitions per chapter.\
Assembly Compiler \'97 loads approved atoms from the pool and fills each slot deterministically (SHA256-based selection). Enforces emotional intensity curves, no atom reuse, and arc-first narrative design.\
Slot Resolver \'97 the deterministic selector algorithm. Same inputs always produce the same book.\
Wave Orchestrator \'97 balances batches of ~60 books so they don't feel repetitive across a catalog (varies arcs, emotional bands, exercise patterns).\
Key subsystems around that core: a naming generator for titles/subtitles, an exercise overlay system (persona/topic token substitution without changing meaning), a freebie renderer (HTML/PDF lead magnets), and a deep QA layer with 68 CI gates that validate everything from emotional escalation to forbidden resolution language ("you've got this," "healed," "cured" are all banned).\
\
What makes it distinctive: V4 treats therapeutic content like safety-critical software. It won't let a book ship with flat emotional arcs, missing identity progression, unresolved symbolic callbacks, or exercises that promise outcomes. Every atom must leave pain unresolved \'97 no premature reassurance. The Narrative Amplification Addendum (in your v4_system_up_spec) layers on five additional enforcement modules: mechanism depth escalation, cost gradients, callback integrity, identity shift tracking, and macro-cadence wave control.\
\
In short \'97 V4 is the engine that lets Phoenix Omega scale to thousands of books while keeping every one therapeutically safe, narratively compelling, and authentically human-voiced.\
