Step 3: Band distribution per file. Every 20-atom file needs band variety: roughly 1\'d7 band 1, 4\'d7 band 2, 7\'d7 band 3, 5\'d7 band 4, 3\'d7 band 5. The compiler needs at least 3 distinct bands. I'd tag bands during writing, not after \'97 the band determines how hot the prose runs. A band 1 recognition is mild ("the email notification pings; a brief tightness in the chest, then it passes"). A band 5 recognition is crisis ("the room is spinning; she can't feel her hands; the words on the screen aren't words anymore").\
