Step 5: The four-role escalation arc within each 20-atom set. RECOGNITION (5 atoms): the pattern appears, the person doesn't yet see it. MECHANISM_PROOF (5): the pattern repeats reliably, the system's logic becomes visible. TURNING_POINT (5): new information changes the relationship to the pattern \'97 not fixes it, changes the relationship to it. EMBODIMENT (5): the person acts alongside the pattern, imperfectly, without the pattern dissolving. Each role is a deeper cut. The atoms within a role are variants, not a sequence \'97 atom v01 and v05 of RECOGNITION are parallel options, not chapter 1 and chapter 5.\
