# 14. Emotional Force Thresholds\
\
Structural validation ensures correct build. Emotional force validation ensures the book moves the listener.\
\
## 14.1 Chapter Temperature Classification\
\
| Phase | Temperature | Intensity | Requirements |\
|-------|-------------|-----------|--------------|\
| HARDSHIP | Hot | 4\'965 | Grounding verbs, body states, visible consequence |\
| HELP | Warm | 2\'963 | Teaching clarity, mechanism naming |\
| HEALING | Warm-Hot | 3\'964 | Emergence verbs, sensory present, no resolution |\
| HOPE | Cool | 1\'962 | Integration, quiet, synthesis |\
\
## 14.2 HARDSHIP Chapter Requirements (Hot)\
\
**Grounding verbs (\uc0\u8805  2):** collapse, shatter, fragment, dissolve, abandon, crumble, unravel, break, fall, lose.\
\
**Body state words (\uc0\u8805  2):** tight, numb, hollow, frozen, raw, clenched, heavy, empty, small, trapped.\
