\
**Emergence verbs (\uc0\u8805  2):** soften, open, return, notice, allow, settle, land, release, breathe, feel.\
\
**Sensory present words (\uc0\u8805  3):** breath, skin, ground, warmth, weight, texture, contact, sound, pulse, surface.\
