# 15. Spiritual Authenticity Gates\
\
Protection against spiritual clich\'e9s, abstract drift, and voice contamination.\
\
## 15.1 Clich\'e9 Density Threshold\
\
No chapter may contain > 2 monitored clich\'e9 phrases.\
\
**Monitored:** "Everything happens for a reason," "Trust the universe," "Divine timing," "Holding space," "Sacred container," "Come into alignment," "Do the work," "Sit with" (overused), "Embodiment" (> 3x/chapter), "Nervous system" (> 4x/chapter without fresh context).\
\
**Gate S01:** > 2 phrases per chapter \uc0\u8594  hard fail.\
**Gate S02:** Phrase in > 30% of catalog \uc0\u8594  warn.\
\
**Exception:** Clich\'e9 allowed if immediately followed by grounding/specificity, or if doctrine-locked for that teacher.\
\
## 15.2 Abstract Noun Ceiling\
\
Max 8 abstract nouns per 200 words. Monitored: consciousness, awareness, presence, energy, frequency, vibration, alignment, wholeness, integration, embodiment, authenticity.\
\
**Gate S03:** > 8 per 200 words \uc0\u8594  warn. > 12 \u8594  hard fail.\
\
## 15.3 Teacher Voice Bleed Detection\
\
If Teacher A's signature phrase appears in Teacher B's book \uc0\u8594  contamination.\
\
