Profiles define allowed_language and forbidden_language tags. Prose must stay within allowed bands and must not use forbidden patterns. Detection is pattern-based (first-person density, command density, academic markers, slang, mystical absolutism). Writer Spec \'a7\'a71\'9623 unchanged; this section adds a compliance layer validated in CI.\
